<p><a href="http://images.ifanr.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/iPad.jpg" rel="lightbox[561966]"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-561974" src="http://images.ifanr.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/iPad.jpg" alt="iPad" width="750" height="584" /></a></p>
